ine and energy&#8221; (2030 Agenda for Sustainable Development by the UN).<\/i><\/span><\/p>\n<\/blockquote>\n<p>[\/et_pb_blurb][\/et_pb_column][\/et_pb_row][et_pb_row column_structure=&#8221;1_2,1_2&#8243; use_custom_gutter=&#8221;on&#8221; gutter_width=&#8221;2&#8243; make_equal=&#8221;on&#8221; _builder_version=&#8221;4.11.4&#8243; _module_preset=&#8221;default&#8221; module_alignment=&#8221;center&#8221; module_alignment_tablet=&#8221;center&#8221; module_alignment_phone=&#8221;center&#8221; module_alignment_last_edited=&#8221;on|desktop&#8221; global_colors_info=&#8221;{}&#8221;][et_pb_column type=&#8221;1_2&#8243; _builder_version=&#8221;4.10.5&#8243; _module_preset=&#8221;default&#8221; global_colors_info=&#8221;{}&#8221;][et_pb_blurb _builder_version=&#8221;4.13.0&#8243; _module_preset=&#8221;default&#8221; body_font_size=&#8221;16px&#8221; custom_margin=&#8221;|||92px|false|false&#8221; custom_margin_tablet=&#8221;|||0px|false|false&#8221; custom_margin_phone=&#8221;|||0px|false|false&#8221; custom_margin_last_edited=&#8221;on|desktop&#8221; custom_padding=&#8221;|30px||30px|false|true&#8221; global_colors_info=&#8221;{}&#8221;]<\/p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong><span data-token-index=\"0\" class=\"notion-enable-hover\" data-reactroot=\"\">Design <\/span><\/strong>&#8211; technologies need to adapt to an individual&#8217;s learning and physical abilities. Around <a href=\"https:\/\/www.un.org\/development\/desa\/disabilities\/resources\/factsheet-on-persons-with-disabilities.html\" class=\"notion-link-token notion-enable-hover\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" data-token-index=\"2\" data-reactroot=\"\"><span class=\"link-annotation-unknown-block-id-1499258446\">15% of the world&#8217;s population<\/span><\/a> (some <span data-token-index=\"4\" class=\"notion-enable-hover\" data-reactroot=\"\">1 Billion people<\/span>) live with some form of <span data-token-index=\"6\" class=\"notion-enable-hover\" data-reactroot=\"\">disability<\/span>. In the US, <a href=\"https:\/\/www.pewresearch.org\/fact-tank\/2017\/04\/07\/disabled-americans-are-less-likely-to-use-technology\/\" class=\"notion-link-token notion-enable-hover\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" data-token-index=\"9\" data-reactroot=\"\">disabled people<\/a><a href=\"https:\/\/www.pewresearch.org\/fact-tank\/2017\/04\/07\/disabled-americans-are-less-likely-to-use-technology\/\" class=\"notion-link-token notion-enable-hover\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" data-token-index=\"10\" data-reactroot=\"\"><span class=\"link-annotation-unknown-block-id--1495225502\"> are <\/span><\/a><a href=\"https:\/\/www.pewresearch.org\/fact-tank\/2017\/04\/07\/disabled-americans-are-less-likely-to-use-technology\/\" class=\"notion-link-token notion-enable-hover\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" data-token-index=\"11\" data-reactroot=\"\"><span class=\"link-annotation-unknown-block-id--1495225502\">less likely <\/span><\/a><a href=\"https:\/\/www.pewresearch.org\/fact-tank\/2017\/04\/07\/disabled-americans-are-less-likely-to-use-technology\/\" class=\"notion-link-token notion-enable-hover\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" data-token-index=\"12\" data-reactroot=\"\"><span class=\"link-annotation-unknown-block-id--1495225502\">to have <\/span><\/a><a href=\"https:\/\/www.pewresearch.org\/fact-tank\/2017\/04\/07\/disabled-americans-are-less-likely-to-use-technology\/\" class=\"notion-link-token notion-enable-hover\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" data-token-index=\"13\" data-reactroot=\"\"><span class=\"link-annotation-unknown-block-id--1495225502\">home broadband service and tech devices<\/span><\/a><span data-token-index=\"14\" class=\"notion-enable-hover\" data-reactroot=\"\"> <\/span>compared to non-disabled people, by roughly<span data-token-index=\"16\" class=\"notion-enable-hover\" data-reactroot=\"\"> 20 percent<\/span>. They are also <span data-token-index=\"18\" class=\"notion-enable-hover\" data-reactroot=\"\">less likely to have a high level of confidence<\/span> in <span data-token-index=\"20\" class=\"notion-enable-hover\" data-reactroot=\"\">using the Internet to keep up with information. <\/span> <span data-token-index=\"22\" class=\"notion-enable-hover\" data-reactroot=\"\">Digital content and applications <\/span>need to account for <span data-token-index=\"24\" class=\"notion-enable-hover\" data-reactroot=\"\">visual, motor, auditory, speech and cognitive disabilities<\/span> in order to provide a more <span data-token-index=\"26\" class=\"notion-enable-hover\" data-reactroot=\"\">inclusive digital environment. <\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p>[\/et_pb_blurb][\/et_pb_column][et_pb_column type=&#8221;1_2&#8243; _builder_version=&#8221;4.10.5&#8243; _module_preset=&#8221;default&#8221; global_colors_info=&#8221;{}&#8221;][et_pb_image src=&#8221;https:\/\/www.grey-box.ca\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/09\/visually-impaired-low-vision.jpg&#8221; title_text=&#8221;Design Guideline for Digital Accessibility by Karwai Pun&#8221; url=&#8221;https:\/\/accessibility.blog.gov.uk\/wp-content\/uploads\/sites\/52\/2016\/09\/visually-impaired-low-vision.png&#8221; url_new_window=&#8221;on&#8221; align=&#8221;center&#8221; align_tablet=&#8221;center&#8221; align_phone=&#8221;center&#8221; align_last_edited=&#8221;on|phone&#8221; _builder_version=&#8221;4.11.4&#8243; _module_preset=&#8221;default&#8221; width_tablet=&#8221;&#8221; width_phone=&#8221;&#8221; width_last_edited=&#8221;on|desktop&#8221; module_alignment=&#8221;center&#8221; module_alignment_tablet=&#8221;center&#8221; module_alignment_phone=&#8221;center&#8221; module_alignment_last_edited=&#8221;on|desktop&#8221; global_colors_info=&#8221;{}&#8221;][\/et_pb_image][\/et_pb_column][\/et_pb_row][et_pb_row column_structure=&#8221;3_5,2_5&#8243; use_custom_gutter=&#8221;on&#8221; gutter_width=&#8221;2&#8243; make_equal=&#8221;on&#8221; _builder_version=&#8221;4.11.4&#8243; _module_preset=&#8221;default&#8221; module_alignment=&#8221;center&#8221; module_alignment_tablet=&#8221;center&#8221; module_alignment_phone=&#8221;center&#8221; module_alignment_last_edited=&#8221;on|desktop&#8221; global_colors_info=&#8221;{}&#8221;][et_pb_column type=&#8221;3_5&#8243; _builder_version=&#8221;4.10.5&#8243; _module_preset=&#8221;default&#8221; global_colors_info=&#8221;{}&#8221;][et_pb_blurb _builder_version=&#8221;4.13.0&#8243; _module_preset=&#8221;default&#8221; body_font_size=&#8221;16px&#8221; custom_margin=&#8221;|||92px|false|false&#8221; custom_margin_tablet=&#8221;|||0px|false|false&#8221; custom_margin_phone=&#8221;|||0px|false|false&#8221; custom_margin_last_edited=&#8221;on|desktop&#8221; custom_padding=&#8221;|30px||30px|false|true&#8221; global_colors_info=&#8221;{}&#8221;]<\/p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong><span data-token-index=\"0\" class=\"notion-enable-hover\" data-reactroot=\"\">Institutional <\/span><\/strong>&#8211; locations where Internet access is offered, whether it be via homes, schools, community centers, religious institutions, coffee shops, or workplaces. <span data-token-index=\"2\" class=\"notion-enable-hover\" data-reactroot=\"\">Students in the Guinean capital Conakry<\/span> are <span data-token-index=\"4\" class=\"notion-enable-hover\" data-reactroot=\"\">unable to study at home <\/span>due to <span data-token-index=\"6\" class=\"notion-enable-hover\" data-reactroot=\"\">constant power cuts<\/span>, leaving them with no choice but to<a href=\"https:\/\/observers.france24.com\/en\/20130603-power-blackouts-guineans-study-gas-stations\" class=\"notion-link-token notion-enable-hover\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" data-token-index=\"8\" data-reactroot=\"\"><span class=\"link-annotation-unknown-block-id--453984414\"> <\/span><\/a><a href=\"https:\/\/observers.france24.com\/en\/20130603-power-blackouts-guineans-study-gas-stations\" class=\"notion-link-token notion-enable-hover\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" data-token-index=\"9\" data-reactroot=\"\"><span class=\"link-annotation-unknown-block-id--453984414\">take their studies <\/span><\/a><span data-token-index=\"10\" class=\"notion-enable-hover\" data-reactroot=\"\">into the streets,<\/span> where there are streetlamps that light up.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p>[\/et_pb_blurb][\/et_pb_column][et_pb_column type=&#8221;2_5&#8243; _builder_version=&#8221;4.10.5&#8243; _module_preset=&#8221;default&#8221; global_colors_info=&#8221;{}&#8221;][et_pb_image src=&#8221;https:\/\/www.grey-box.ca\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/09\/the_dark_side_of_education.jpg&#8221; title_text=&#8221;The Dark Side of Education by Rebecca Blackwell&#8221; align=&#8221;center&#8221; _builder_version=&#8221;4.11.4&#8243; _module_preset=&#8221;default&#8221; module_alignment=&#8221;center&#8221; module_alignment_tablet=&#8221;center&#8221; module_alignment_phone=&#8221;center&#8221; module_alignment_last_edited=&#8221;on|desktop&#8221; global_colors_info=&#8221;{}&#8221;][\/et_pb_image][\/et_pb_column][\/et_pb_row][et_pb_row column_structure=&#8221;3_5,2_5&#8243; use_custom_gutter=&#8221;on&#8221; gutter_width=&#8221;2&#8243; make_equal=&#8221;on&#8221; _builder_version=&#8221;4.11.4&#8243; _module_preset=&#8221;default&#8221; module_alignment=&#8221;center&#8221; module_alignment_tablet=&#8221;center&#8221; module_alignment_phone=&#8221;center&#8221; module_alignment_last_edited=&#8221;on|desktop&#8221; global_colors_info=&#8221;{}&#8221;][et_pb_column type=&#8221;3_5&#8243; _builder_version=&#8221;4.10.5&#8243; _module_preset=&#8221;default&#8221; global_colors_info=&#8221;{}&#8221;][et_pb_blurb _builder_version=&#8221;4.13.0&#8243; _module_preset=&#8221;default&#8221; body_font_size=&#8221;16px&#8221; custom_margin=&#8221;|||92px|false|false&#8221; custom_margin_tablet=&#8221;|||0px|false|false&#8221; custom_margin_phone=&#8221;|||0px|false|false&#8221; custom_margin_last_edited=&#8221;on|desktop&#8221; custom_padding=&#8221;|30px||30px|false|true&#8221; global_colors_info=&#8221;{}&#8221;]<\/p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong><span data-token-index=\"0\" class=\"notion-enable-hover\" data-reactroot=\"\">Political <\/span><\/strong>&#8211; broadly speaking, forms of Internet censorship. In <span data-token-index=\"2\" class=\"notion-enable-hover\" data-reactroot=\"\">Cuba<\/span>, people are keeping up with world news, entertainment and culture through a weekly package called <a href=\"https:\/\/www.cbc.ca\/news\/world\/cuba-el-paquete-internet-wifi-havana-1.3527274\" class=\"notion-link-token notion-enable-hover\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" index=\"4\" reactroot=\"\"><span class=\"link-annotation-unknown-block-id--1004595648\">&#8216;El Paquete&#8217;<\/span><\/a><span data-token-index=\"5\" class=\"notion-enable-hover\" data-reactroot=\"\"> <\/span>as an <span data-token-index=\"7\" class=\"notion-enable-hover\" data-reactroot=\"\">alternative to the Internet<\/span>. The nation relies on an underground <span data-token-index=\"9\" class=\"notion-enable-hover\" data-reactroot=\"\">Sneakernet <\/span>system in which data and electronic files are transferred between machines through storage devices that are physically transported on foot rather than over the Internet. Such distribution workaround of physical copies of digital content from person to person is rooted in an <span data-token-index=\"11\" class=\"notion-enable-hover\" data-reactroot=\"\">underdeveloped infrastructure<\/span> and <span data-token-index=\"13\" class=\"notion-enable-hover\" data-reactroot=\"\">government censorship of Western culture.<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p>[\/et_pb_blurb][\/et_pb_column][et_pb_column type=&#8221;2_5&#8243; _builder_version=&#8221;4.10.5&#8243; _module_preset=&#8221;default&#8221; global_colors_info=&#8221;{}&#8221;][et_pb_image src=&#8221;https:\/\/www.grey-box.ca\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/09\/el_paquete-scaled.jpg&#8221; title_text=&#8221;El paquete semanal, the &#8216;Internet hard drive&#8217; by Lisette Poole&#8221; align=&#8221;center&#8221; align_tablet=&#8221;center&#8221; align_phone=&#8221;center&#8221; align_last_edited=&#8221;on|desktop&#8221; _builder_version=&#8221;4.11.4&#8243; _module_preset=&#8221;default&#8221; module_alignment=&#8221;center&#8221; module_alignment_tablet=&#8221;center&#8221; module_alignment_phone=&#8221;center&#8221; module_alignment_last_edited=&#8221;on|phone&#8221; global_colors_info=&#8221;{}&#8221;][\/et_pb_image][\/et_pb_column][\/et_pb_row][et_pb_row _builder_version=&#8221;4.10.5&#8243; _module_preset=&#8221;default&#8221; global_colors_info=&#8221;{}&#8221;][et_pb_column type=&#8221;4_4&#8243; _builder_version=&#8221;4.10.5&#8243; _module_preset=&#8221;default&#8221; global_colors_info=&#8221;{}&#8221;][et_pb_blurb title=&#8221;Education x Digital Divide&#8221; _builder_version=&#8221;4.13.0&#8243; _module_preset=&#8221;default&#8221; header_font=&#8221;|600|||||||&#8221; header_font_size=&#8221;20px&#8221; body_font_size=&#8221;16px&#8221; module_alignment=&#8221;center&#8221; custom_padding=&#8221;|30px||30px|false|true&#8221; module_alignment_tablet=&#8221;center&#8221; module_alignment_phone=&#8221;center&#8221; module_alignment_last_edited=&#8221;on|desktop&#8221; global_colors_info=&#8221;{}&#8221;]<\/p>\n<p>In 2018, it was estimated that one-in-six children, adolescents and youths were out-of-school. That figure represents <a href=\"http:\/\/uis.unesco.org\/sites\/default\/files\/documents\/new-methodology-shows-258-million-children-adolescents-and-youth-are-out-school.pdf\">over 258 Million<\/a> school-age-children globally. This learning crisis can be explained by: (1) lack of access to education, (2) failure to keep track of and retain children to progress through the system, and (3) low quality of education. Subsequently, these learners are excluded from gaining employable skills and from accessing better socio-economic opportunities, thus reducing their chance to break the poverty cycle.<\/p>\n<p>This educational gap is further exacerbated by COVID-19, as UNESCO Associated Schools Network reported that at the outbreak of the pandemic, <a href=\"https:\/\/en.unesco.org\/covid19\/educationresponse\">over 160 countries closed their educational premises, affecting over 1.4B students<\/a>. In some countries such as Canada and the United States, schools and post-secondary institutions have been closed for over 50 weeks. This furthers the existing gap, leaving the already-marginalized learners to be even more vulnerable to economic hinderances.<\/p>\n<p>Technology plays a critical role in the transition from traditional classrooms to remote learning to a hybrid model. Learning resources are widely available to educators and learners, however, access to those digital resources are not as easy and seamless.<\/p>\n<p>[\/et_pb_blurb][\/et_pb_column][\/et_pb_row][et_pb_row column_structure=&#8221;3_5,2_5&#8243; use_custom_gutter=&#8221;on&#8221; gutter_width=&#8221;2&#8243; make_equal=&#8221;on&#8221; _builder_version=&#8221;4.11.4&#8243; _module_preset=&#8221;default&#8221; module_alignment=&#8221;center&#8221; module_alignment_tablet=&#8221;center&#8221; module_alignment_phone=&#8221;center&#8221; module_alignment_last_edited=&#8221;on|desktop&#8221; global_colors_info=&#8221;{}&#8221;][et_pb_column type=&#8221;3_5&#8243; _builder_version=&#8221;4.10.5&#8243; _module_preset=&#8221;default&#8221; global_colors_info=&#8221;{}&#8221;][et_pb_blurb _builder_version=&#8221;4.13.0&#8243; _module_preset=&#8221;default&#8221; body_font_size=&#8221;16px&#8221; custom_margin=&#8221;|||90px|false|false&#8221; custom_margin_tablet=&#8221;|||0px|false|false&#8221; custom_margin_phone=&#8221;|||0px|false|false&#8221; custom_margin_last_edited=&#8221;on|desktop&#8221; custom_padding=&#8221;|30px||30px|false|true&#8221; global_colors_info=&#8221;{}&#8221;]<\/p>\n<p>During a recent business trip to Morocco, Grey-box&#8217;s founder Valentin Kravtchenko interviewed a few local students about their experiences with remote learning. A group of young students highlighted the difficulty to follow a class that required merging multiples groups into one session (with up to 750 students in the same video call, but with attendance levels as low as 50 people per session). Some teachers would even turn off their own cameras while students watched an unengaging slideshow that was difficult to follow along with. Thus, the students would sometimes simply record the lecture to watch later or be distracted by their phones next to them.<\/p>\n<p>[\/et_pb_blurb][\/et_pb_column][et_pb_column type=&#8221;2_5&#8243; _builder_version=&#8221;4.10.5&#8243; _module_preset=&#8221;default&#8221; global_colors_info=&#8221;{}&#8221;][et_pb_image src=&#8221;https:\/\/www.grey-box.ca\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/09\/1_school_entrance.jpg&#8221; title_text=&#8221;Morroccan Middle School by Gareth Smail&#8221; _builder_version=&#8221;4.10.5&#8243; _module_preset=&#8221;default&#8221; global_colors_info=&#8221;{}&#8221;][\/et_pb_image][\/et_pb_column][\/et_pb_row][et_pb_row _builder_version=&#8221;4.10.5&#8243; _module_preset=&#8221;default&#8221; global_colors_info=&#8221;{}&#8221;][et_pb_column type=&#8221;4_4&#8243; _builder_version=&#8221;4.10.5&#8243; _module_preset=&#8221;default&#8221; global_colors_info=&#8221;{}&#8221;][et_pb_text _builder_version=&#8221;4.11.4&#8243; _module_preset=&#8221;default&#8221; text_font=&#8221;|600|||||||&#8221; text_font_size=&#8221;20px&#8221; header_4_font=&#8221;|600|||||||&#8221; custom_margin=&#8221;||||false|false&#8221; custom_padding=&#8221;|30px||30px|false|true&#8221; global_colors_info=&#8221;{}&#8221;]<\/p>\n<p><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Recommendations and Solutions<\/span><\/p>\n<p>[\/et_pb_text][et_pb_blurb title=&#8221;Initiatives bridging the digital divide in education&#8221; _builder_version=&#8221;4.13.0&#8243; _module_preset=&#8221;default&#8221; header_font=&#8221;|600|||||||&#8221; header_font_size=&#8221;20px&#8221; body_font_size=&#8221;16px&#8221; custom_padding=&#8221;|30px||30px|false|true&#8221; global_colors_info=&#8221;{}&#8221;]<\/p>\n<p>In order to bridge the digital divide and provide equitable access to digital resources for isolated and remote populations, we turn to a few innovative initiatives that are actively addressing this issue.<\/p>\n<p>[\/et_pb_blurb][\/et_pb_column][\/et_pb_row][et_pb_row column_structure=&#8221;3_5,2_5&#8243; use_custom_gutter=&#8221;on&#8221; gutter_width=&#8221;2&#8243; make_equal=&#8221;on&#8221; _builder_version=&#8221;4.11.4&#8243; _module_preset=&#8221;default&#8221; module_alignment=&#8221;center&#8221; module_alignment_tablet=&#8221;center&#8221; module_alignment_phone=&#8221;center&#8221; module_alignment_last_edited=&#8221;on|desktop&#8221; global_colors_info=&#8221;{}&#8221;][et_pb_column type=&#8221;3_5&#8243; _builder_version=&#8221;4.10.5&#8243; _module_preset=&#8221;default&#8221; global_colors_info=&#8221;{}&#8221;][et_pb_blurb title=&#8221;1. La Puce (increase digital literacy skills)&#8221; _builder_version=&#8221;4.13.0&#8243; _module_preset=&#8221;default&#8221; body_font_size=&#8221;16px&#8221; custom_margin=&#8221;|||90px|false|false&#8221; custom_margin_tablet=&#8221;|||0px|false|false&#8221; custom_margin_phone=&#8221;|||0px|false|false&#8221; custom_margin_last_edited=&#8221;on|desktop&#8221; custom_padding=&#8221;|30px||30px|false|true&#8221; global_colors_info=&#8221;{}&#8221;]<\/p>\n<p>La Puce is a Montreal-based organization founded in 1984, that specialized in providing training courses to the general public, covering the use of computers, the Internet, desktop applications tools, online collaborative tools, and digital communications tools. One of their programs, <a href=\"https:\/\/lapuce.org\/programmes\/citoyens-branches\/\" class=\"notion-link-token notion-enable-hover\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" data-token-index=\"1\" data-reactroot=\"\"><span class=\"link-annotation-unknown-block-id--820905010\">&#8216;Connected Citizens&#8217;<\/span><\/a>, aims to integrate seniors into the increasingly digitized world by pairing them up with young people who are proficient in using various technologies. In addition, the organization offers a job-readiness training program focusing on the development of digital skills to those who are disconnected from the job market and who are in the process of professional integration.<\/p>\n<p>[\/et_pb_blurb][\/et_pb_column][et_pb_column type=&#8221;2_5&#8243; _builder_version=&#8221;4.10.5&#8243; _module_preset=&#8221;default&#8221; global_colors_info=&#8221;{}&#8221;][et_pb_image src=&#8221;https:\/\/www.grey-box.ca\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/05\/cropped-cropped-LAPUCE_LOGO_COULEUR_RVB-300&#215;79-1.png&#8221; title_text=&#8221;cropped-cropped-LAPUCE_LOGO_COULEUR_RVB-300&#215;79-1&#8243; align=&#8221;center&#8221; align_tablet=&#8221;center&#8221; align_phone=&#8221;center&#8221; align_last_edited=&#8221;on|desktop&#8221; _builder_version=&#8221;4.11.4&#8243; _module_preset=&#8221;default&#8221; max_width=&#8221;75%&#8221; max_width_tablet=&#8221;50%&#8221; max_width_phone=&#8221;75%&#8221; max_width_last_edited=&#8221;on|desktop&#8221; module_alignment=&#8221;center&#8221; global_colors_info=&#8221;{}&#8221;][\/et_pb_image][\/et_pb_column][\/et_pb_row][et_pb_row column_structure=&#8221;3_5,2_5&#8243; use_custom_gutter=&#8221;on&#8221; gutter_width=&#8221;2&#8243; make_equal=&#8221;on&#8221; _builder_version=&#8221;4.11.4&#8243; _module_preset=&#8221;default&#8221; module_alignment=&#8221;center&#8221; module_alignment_tablet=&#8221;center&#8221; module_alignment_phone=&#8221;center&#8221; module_alignment_last_edited=&#8221;on|desktop&#8221; global_colors_info=&#8221;{}&#8221;][et_pb_column type=&#8221;3_5&#8243; _builder_version=&#8221;4.10.5&#8243; _module_preset=&#8221;default&#8221; global_colors_info=&#8221;{}&#8221;][et_pb_blurb title=&#8221;2. Khan Academy (open source education)&#8221; _builder_version=&#8221;4.13.0&#8243; _module_preset=&#8221;default&#8221; body_font_size=&#8221;16px&#8221; custom_margin=&#8221;|||90px|false|false&#8221; custom_margin_tablet=&#8221;|||0px|false|false&#8221; custom_margin_phone=&#8221;|||0px|false|false&#8221; custom_margin_last_edited=&#8221;on|desktop&#8221; custom_padding=&#8221;|30px||30px|false|true&#8221; global_colors_info=&#8221;{}&#8221;]<\/p>\n<p>Khan Academy is an online educational hub that provides free courses, lessons and practice to students and educators all around the world. It offers content in the field of mathematics, computer programming, arts, economics, physics, chemistry, biology, medicine, finance, history, and more. This nonprofit organization produces its lesson content in the form of videos and as well as supplementary exercises. To date, the digital learning platform has reached <a href=\"https:\/\/www.cnbc.com\/video\/2021\/03\/02\/khan-academy-founder-on-bridging-the-digital-divide-during-covid.html\" class=\"notion-link-token notion-enable-hover\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" data-token-index=\"1\" data-reactroot=\"\"><span class=\"link-annotation-unknown-block-id-1474997507\">120M students<\/span><\/a> around the world with free educational content available in 50 languages.<\/p>\n<p>[\/et_pb_blurb][\/et_pb_column][et_pb_column type=&#8221;2_5&#8243; _builder_version=&#8221;4.10.5&#8243; _module_preset=&#8221;default&#8221; global_colors_info=&#8221;{}&#8221;][et_pb_image src=&#8221;https:\/\/www.grey-box.ca\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/09\/kh.jpg&#8221; title_text=&#8221;Khan Academy Logo&#8221; align=&#8221;center&#8221; align_tablet=&#8221;center&#8221; align_phone=&#8221;center&#8221; align_last_edited=&#8221;on|desktop&#8221; _builder_version=&#8221;4.11.4&#8243; _module_preset=&#8221;default&#8221; max_width=&#8221;75%&#8221; max_width_tablet=&#8221;50%&#8221; max_width_phone=&#8221;75%&#8221; max_width_last_edited=&#8221;on|desktop&#8221; module_alignment=&#8221;center&#8221; global_colors_info=&#8221;{}&#8221;][\/et_pb_image][\/et_pb_column][\/et_pb_row][et_pb_row column_structure=&#8221;3_5,2_5&#8243; use_custom_gutter=&#8221;on&#8221; gutter_width=&#8221;2&#8243; make_equal=&#8221;on&#8221; _builder_version=&#8221;4.11.4&#8243; _module_preset=&#8221;default&#8221; module_alignment=&#8221;center&#8221; module_alignment_tablet=&#8221;center&#8221; module_alignment_phone=&#8221;center&#8221; module_alignment_last_edited=&#8221;on|desktop&#8221; global_colors_info=&#8221;{}&#8221;][et_pb_column type=&#8221;3_5&#8243; _builder_version=&#8221;4.10.5&#8243; _module_preset=&#8221;default&#8221; global_colors_info=&#8221;{}&#8221;][et_pb_blurb title=&#8221;3. ReBOOT Canada (refurbished computers)&#8221; _builder_version=&#8221;4.13.0&#8243; _module_preset=&#8221;default&#8221; body_font_size=&#8221;16px&#8221; custom_margin=&#8221;|||90px|false|false&#8221; custom_margin_tablet=&#8221;|||0px|false|false&#8221; custom_margin_phone=&#8221;|||0px|false|false&#8221; custom_margin_last_edited=&#8221;on|desktop&#8221; custom_padding=&#8221;|30px||30px|false|true&#8221; global_colors_info=&#8221;{}&#8221;]<\/p>\n<p>Based in Toronto, ReBOOT was founded in 1995 to prove refurbished computers for at-risk youth, seniors, community organizations, registered charities and not-for-profit groups, at a low cost through their ReSTART and ReSOURCE programs. In addition, they run a free Wi-fi program throughout several neighbourhoods in Toronto. With such programs, students from low-income neighbourhoods reported having a better educational experience when completing assignments and studying outside of schools.<\/p>\n<p>[\/et_pb_blurb][\/et_pb_column][et_pb_column type=&#8221;2_5&#8243; _builder_version=&#8221;4.10.5&#8243; _module_preset=&#8221;default&#8221; global_colors_info=&#8221;{}&#8221;][et_pb_image src=&#8221;https:\/\/www.grey-box.ca\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/09\/483-4834442_reboot-canada-circle-hd-png-download.jpg&#8221; title_text=&#8221;Reboot Canada Logo&#8221; align=&#8221;center&#8221; align_tablet=&#8221;center&#8221; align_phone=&#8221;center&#8221; align_last_edited=&#8221;on|desktop&#8221; _builder_version=&#8221;4.11.4&#8243; _module_preset=&#8221;default&#8221; max_width=&#8221;75%&#8221; max_width_tablet=&#8221;50%&#8221; max_width_phone=&#8221;75%&#8221; max_width_last_edited=&#8221;on|tablet&#8221; module_alignment=&#8221;center&#8221; global_colors_info=&#8221;{}&#8221;][\/et_pb_image][\/et_pb_column][\/et_pb_row][et_pb_row column_structure=&#8221;3_5,2_5&#8243; use_custom_gutter=&#8221;on&#8221; gutter_width=&#8221;2&#8243; make_equal=&#8221;on&#8221; _builder_version=&#8221;4.11.4&#8243; _module_preset=&#8221;default&#8221; module_alignment=&#8221;center&#8221; module_alignment_tablet=&#8221;center&#8221; module_alignment_phone=&#8221;center&#8221; module_alignment_last_edited=&#8221;on|desktop&#8221; global_colors_info=&#8221;{}&#8221;][et_pb_column type=&#8221;3_5&#8243; _builder_version=&#8221;4.10.5&#8243; _module_preset=&#8221;default&#8221; global_colors_info=&#8221;{}&#8221;][et_pb_blurb title=&#8221;4. TechSoup Canada (discounted software)&#8221; _builder_version=&#8221;4.13.0&#8243; _module_preset=&#8221;default&#8221; body_font_size=&#8221;16px&#8221; custom_margin=&#8221;|||90px|false|false&#8221; custom_margin_tablet=&#8221;|||0px|false|false&#8221; custom_margin_phone=&#8221;|||0px|false|false&#8221; custom_margin_last_edited=&#8221;on|desktop&#8221; custom_padding=&#8221;|30px||30px|false|true&#8221; global_colors_info=&#8221;{}&#8221;]<\/p>\n<p>As part of the global nonprofit organization TechSoup, TechSoup Canada provides low-cost access to donated and discounted software such as Microsoft Office and Adobe Creative Cloud, to qualified charities, nonprofit organizations and libraries. By connecting organizations with affordable technologies, TechSoup gives organizations the opportunity to strategically allocate resources to other key areas.<\/p>\n<p>[\/et_pb_blurb][\/et_pb_column][et_pb_column type=&#8221;2_5&#8243; _builder_version=&#8221;4.10.5&#8243; _module_preset=&#8221;default&#8221; global_colors_info=&#8221;{}&#8221;][et_pb_image src=&#8221;https:\/\/www.grey-box.ca\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/09\/schema-techsoup-logo.jpg&#8221; title_text=&#8221;Techsoup Logo&#8221; align=&#8221;center&#8221; align_tablet=&#8221;center&#8221; align_phone=&#8221;center&#8221; align_last_edited=&#8221;on|desktop&#8221; _builder_version=&#8221;4.11.4&#8243; _module_preset=&#8221;default&#8221; max_width=&#8221;75%&#8221; max_width_tablet=&#8221;50%&#8221; max_width_phone=&#8221;75%&#8221; max_width_last_edited=&#8221;on|desktop&#8221; module_alignment=&#8221;center&#8221; global_colors_info=&#8221;{}&#8221;][\/et_pb_image][\/et_pb_column][\/et_pb_row][et_pb_row column_structure=&#8221;3_5,2_5&#8243; use_custom_gutter=&#8221;on&#8221; gutter_width=&#8221;2&#8243; make_equal=&#8221;on&#8221; _builder_version=&#8221;4.11.4&#8243; _module_preset=&#8221;default&#8221; module_alignment=&#8221;center&#8221; module_alignment_tablet=&#8221;center&#8221; module_alignment_phone=&#8221;center&#8221; module_alignment_last_edited=&#8221;on|desktop&#8221; global_colors_info=&#8221;{}&#8221;][et_pb_column type=&#8221;3_5&#8243; _builder_version=&#8221;4.10.5&#8243; _module_preset=&#8221;default&#8221; global_colors_info=&#8221;{}&#8221;][et_pb_blurb title=&#8221;5. Grey-box (offline access to digital resources)&#8221; _builder_version=&#8221;4.13.0&#8243; _module_preset=&#8221;default&#8221; body_font_size=&#8221;16px&#8221; custom_margin=&#8221;|||90px|false|false&#8221; custom_margin_tablet=&#8221;|||0px|false|false&#8221; custom_margin_phone=&#8221;|||0px|false|false&#8221; custom_margin_last_edited=&#8221;on|desktop&#8221; custom_padding=&#8221;|30px||30px|false|true&#8221; global_colors_info=&#8221;{}&#8221;]<\/p>\n<p>Grey-box is a social innovation startup in the research and development phase. Its main product &#8211; UNI &#8211; is a portable hotspot that provides wireless access to pre-loaded digital resources such as Wikipedia and Khan Academy in areas where Internet access is unreliable. With technology like Grey-box, nonprofit organizations such as La Puce can increase their net social impact by reaching populations in more remote areas.<\/p>\n<p>[\/et_pb_blurb][\/et_pb_column][et_pb_column type=&#8221;2_5&#8243; _builder_version=&#8221;4.10.5&#8243; _module_preset=&#8221;default&#8221; global_colors_info=&#8221;{}&#8221;][et_pb_image src=&#8221;https:\/\/www.grey-box.ca\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/05\/logoGREY-BOX.jpg&#8221; title_text=&#8221;logoGREY-BOX&#8221; align=&#8221;center&#8221; align_tablet=&#8221;center&#8221; align_phone=&#8221;center&#8221; align_last_edited=&#8221;on|desktop&#8221; _builder_version=&#8221;4.11.4&#8243; _module_preset=&#8221;default&#8221; max_width=&#8221;50%&#8221; max_width_tablet=&#8221;30%&#8221; max_width_phone=&#8221;30%&#8221; max_width_last_edited=&#8221;on|desktop&#8221; module_alignment=&#8221;center&#8221; global_colors_info=&#8221;{}&#8221;][\/et_pb_image][\/et_pb_column][\/et_pb_row][et_pb_row _builder_version=&#8221;4.10.5&#8243; _module_preset=&#8221;default&#8221; global_colors_info=&#8221;{}&#8221;][et_pb_column type=&#8221;4_4&#8243; _builder_version=&#8221;4.10.5&#8243; _module_preset=&#8221;default&#8221; global_colors_info=&#8221;{}&#8221;][et_pb_blurb title=&#8221;Conclusion&#8221; _builder_version=&#8221;4.13.0&#8243; _module_preset=&#8221;default&#8221; header_font=&#8221;|600|||||||&#8221; header_font_size=&#8221;20px&#8221; body_font_size=&#8221;16px&#8221; custom_padding=&#8221;|30px||30px|false|true&#8221; global_colors_info=&#8221;{}&#8221;]<\/p>\n<p>The digital divide is a complex and intricate social issue that is present in both developed and developing nations around the world. The magnified digital exclusion that some groups are facing due to the COVID-19 pandemic highlights the urgent need for not only economic and social solutions but also technological initiatives, to bridge the gap between the digital &#8216;haves&#8217; and &#8216;have-nots&#8217;. All things considered, no single entity or organization should work alone to bridge the digital divide &#8211; instead, they should collaborate and benefit from each other&#8217;s expertise to fulfil the overarching mission and help children around the world.<\/p>\n<p>[\/et_pb_blurb][\/et_pb_column][\/et_pb_row][et_pb_row _builder_version=&#8221;4.10.5&#8243; _module_preset=&#8221;default&#8221; global_colors_info=&#8221;{}&#8221;][et_pb_column type=&#8221;4_4&#8243; _builder_version=&#8221;4.10.5&#8243; _module_preset=&#8221;default&#8221; global_colors_info=&#8221;{}&#8221;][et_pb_blurb title=&#8221;Works Cited&#8221; _builder_version=&#8221;4.13.0&#8243; _module_preset=&#8221;default&#8221; header_font=&#8221;|600|||||||&#8221; header_font_size=&#8221;20px&#8221; body_font_size=&#8221;16px&#8221; custom_padding=&#8221;|30px||30px|false|true&#8221; global_colors_info=&#8221;{}&#8221;]<\/p>\n<p><a href=\"https:\/\/www.itu.int\/en\/ITU-D\/Statistics\/Pages\/stat\/default.aspx\">https:\/\/www.itu.int\/en\/ITU-D\/Statistics\/Pages\/stat\/default.aspx<\/a><\/p>\n<p><a href=\"http:\/\/students.cs.uri.edu\/~forensics\/courses\/CSC101\/example_final\/background.html\">http:\/\/students.cs.uri.edu\/~forensics\/courses\/CSC101\/example_final\/background.html<\/a><\/p>\n<p><a href=\"https:\/\/thoughtleadership.rbc.com\/building-bandwidth-preparing-indigenous-youth-for-a-digital-future\/\">https:\/\/thoughtleadership.rbc.com\/building-bandwidth-preparing-indigenous-youth-for-a-digital-future\/<\/a><\/p>\n<p><a href=\"https:\/\/www.cbc.ca\/news\/world\/cuba-el-paquete-internet-wifi-havana-1.3527274\">https:\/\/www.cbc.ca\/news\/world\/cuba-el-paquete-internet-wifi-havana-1.3527274<\/a><\/p>\n<p><a href=\"https:\/\/observers.france24.com\/en\/20130603-power-blackouts-guineans-study-gas-stations\">https:\/\/observers.france24.com\/en\/20130603-power-blackouts-guineans-study-gas-stations<\/a><\/p>\n<p><a href=\"https:\/\/en.unesco.